plot: Monica, Phoebe and Joey advise Rachel to tell the father about the pregnancy. Chandler and Ross lose the wedding photos.

Joey ordered a porn movie in his hotel room at the wedding venue and it appears on bills for every room. Chandler is happy to be married but Monica feels miserable no longer to be a bride, so she can't help herself and opens wedding presents without him. When Ross, who cleaned the reception venue he didn't pick up the disposable wedding photo cameras so all the pictures are gone. He fears Monica will make his and Chandler's life miserable so Ross suggests they fake at least some at another wedding. 'Pregnant' Phoebe was ready to accept Joey's wedding proposal, till Monica tells him that Phoebe is not the expectant mother. Joey finds a sweater which Phoebe considers a clue to the identity of the father. Knowing the truth, Joey also proposes to Rachel.—KGF Vissers

Chandler and Ross lose the pictures of the wedding and try everything they can to stop Monica finding out. Meanwhile Joey finds out who is the real expectant mother. Phoebe and Monica tell Rachel that she have to tell the father about the pregnancy. After a misunderstanding about a shirt, Monica, Phoebe and Joey figure out who is the father of Rachel's baby.—Dodgeps
